$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux Pro board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Terasic DE10-Nano out-of-box demo — individual per-bit signals.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Live peripherals: HDMI raster, audio sine, ADC, etc.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 1 ! led0 $end
$var wire 1 " led1 $end
$var wire 1 # led2 $end
$var wire 1 $ led3 $end
$var wire 1 % led4 $end
$var wire 1 & led5 $end
$var wire 1 ' led6 $end
$var wire 1 ( led7 $end
$var wire 1 ) sw0 $end
$var wire 1 * sw1 $end
$var wire 1 + sw2 $end
$var wire 1 , sw3 $end
$var wire 1 - key0 $end
$var wire 1 . key1 $end
$var wire 16 / hdmi_out_data $end
$var wire 1 0 hdmi_out_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 1 hdmi_out_hsync $end
$var wire 1 2 hdmi_out_vsync $end
$var wire 1 3 hdmi_out_de $end
$var wire 16 4 accel $end
$var wire 12 5 adc_ch0 $end
$var wire 12 6 adc_ch1 $end
$var wire 12 7 adc_ch2 $end
$var wire 12 8 adc_ch3 $end
$var wire 12 9 adc_ch4 $end
$var wire 12 : adc_ch5 $end
$var wire 12 ; adc_ch6 $end
$var wire 12 < adc_ch7 $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
